thread.title: JiaoJiao

author: JiaoJiao
title: JiaoJiao
text: I received the purse that I purchased very fast, it was the next day or two. I was surprised that the shipping was really fast. The only thing I was a little disappointed was I didn't received the original box which I would really wanted one because it's pretty, instead they only put the purse in the original plastic bag and put it in to the shipping box. And the plastic bag was a little dusty too. Other than that, the bag is great, I love it!
